<plot>A shy young man is walking alone through the snow swept streets of the city. The saving paradise in this cold, snowy night are the lit up, warm windows of a video store. The shop insistent Caro is behind the till and when he sees her, he is bowled over. He is stuck in his shyness and can't seem to pick up his courage and speak to her. Only in his dreams can he show of himself what he so sorely misses in reality. In his dreams he is there, cool and relaxed, singing a love song to her. But real life is very different...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?515905</url></doc>
